<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Montaje a Medida | TechRM</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg-color: #0b0c10;
            --bg-panel: #11131a;
            --card-bg: #171923;
            --card-inner: #202431;
            --card-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            --text-main: #ffffff;
            --text-muted: #9ca3af;
            --accent-blue: #7fc7ff;
            --accent-green: #7dd3a8;
            --accent-amber: #f4c56a;
            --nav-bg: rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.95);
            --nav-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-main);
            font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }

        .mount-hero {
            min-height: 620px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(380px, 1.1fr);
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4rem;
            padding: 9rem 6% 5rem;
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 72% 32%, rgba(127, 199, 255, 0.24), transparent 34%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(11, 12, 16, 1) 0%, rgba(9, 18, 30, 0.96) 52%, rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.86) 100%);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--card-border);
        }

        .hero-copy {
            max-width: 720px;
        }

        .eyebrow {
            color: var(--accent-blue);
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 1.5px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
        }

        .mount-hero h1 {
            font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 6vw, 5.4rem);
            line-height: 0.98;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .mount-hero h1 span {
            color: var(--accent-blue);
        }

        .hero-copy p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 620px;
            font-size: 1.08rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }

        .hero-actions {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .btn-service {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 46px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1.35rem;
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            color: var(--text-main);
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            letter-spacing: 0.4px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            cursor: pointer;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: transform 0.2s, border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-service:hover,
        .btn-service:focus {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            border-color: rgba(127, 199, 255, 0.55);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        }

        .btn-primary-service {
            background: var(--accent-blue);
            color: #08233d;
            border-color: transparent;
        }

        .lead-form {
            align-self: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(127, 199, 255, 0.34);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(17, 19, 26, 0.9);
            padding: 1.5rem;
            box-shadow: 0 22px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.28);
            backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        }

        .lead-form h2 {
            font-size: 1.45rem;
            line-height: 1.15;
            margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
        }

        .lead-form p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.1rem;
        }

        .form-row {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 0.8rem;
        }

        .form-group { margin-bottom: 0.85rem; }

        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            color: #d7e9ff;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        input,
        select,
        textarea {
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-family: inherit;
            padding: 0.82rem 0.9rem;
        }

        textarea { resize: vertical; }

        .form-submit {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 46px;
            margin-top: 0.25rem;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: var(--accent-blue);
            color: #08233d;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .success-banner {
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding: 0.8rem 0.9rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(125, 211, 168, 0.42);
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: rgba(125, 211, 168, 0.12);
            color: #bdf4d0;
            font-size: 0.86rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .build-preview {
            align-self: stretch;
            min-height: 420px;
            display: grid;
            align-content: end;
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(23, 25, 35, 0.08), rgba(23, 25, 35, 0.9)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591799264318-7e6ef8ddb7ea?auto=format&fit=crop&q=85&w=1000') center/cover;
            position: relative;
        }

        .build-preview::before {
            content: "";
            position: absolute;
            inset: 1rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(127, 199, 255, 0.28);
            border-radius: 6px;
            background:
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(127, 199, 255, 0.16) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(127, 199, 255, 0.12) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 34px 34px;
            opacity: 0.75;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .preview-content {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            background: rgba(11, 12, 16, 0.78);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
        }

        .preview-content h2 {
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .preview-content p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1180px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 4rem 2rem;
        }

        .section-heading {
            display: flex;
            align-items: end;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .section-heading h2 {
            font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
            line-height: 1.05;
        }

        .section-heading p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 460px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .build-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }

        .build-card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            min-height: 100%;
        }

        .build-card img {
            width: 100%;
            aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
            object-fit: cover;
            filter: saturate(0.96) contrast(1.04);
        }

        .build-card-body {
            padding: 1.35rem;
        }

        .build-tag {
            display: inline-flex;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            padding: 0.25rem 0.65rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: var(--accent-blue);
            color: #08233d;
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            font-weight: 900;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        .build-tag.green { background: var(--accent-green); }
        .build-tag.amber { background: var(--accent-amber); }

        .build-card h3 {
            font-size: 1.18rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
            margin-bottom: 0.7rem;
        }

        .build-card p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.88rem;
        }

        .workflow {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            background: var(--bg-panel);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 2rem;
        }

        .workflow-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        .workflow-step {
            background: var(--card-inner);
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1.1rem;
        }

        .workflow-step strong {
            display: inline-flex;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--accent-blue);
            color: #08233d;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .workflow-step h3 {
            font-size: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .workflow-step p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            font-size: 0.82rem;
        }

        .cta-panel {
            margin-top: 4rem;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr auto;
            gap: 2rem;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(127, 199, 255, 0.14), var(--bg-panel));
            border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .cta-panel h2 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
        }

        .cta-panel p {
            color: var(--text-muted);
            max-width: 720px;
        }

        footer {
            padding: 3rem 6%;
            border-top: 1px solid var(--card-border);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            gap: 1rem;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .light-mode {
            --bg-color: #f7f9fc;
            --bg-panel: #ffffff;
            --card-bg: #f8f9fa;
            --card-inner: #ffffff;
            --card-border: rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.12);
            --text-main: #172033;
            --text-muted: #4b5565;
            --accent-blue: #0b74d1;
            --accent-green: #15803d;
            --accent-amber: #b45309;
            --nav-bg: rgba(248, 249, 250, 0.95);
            --nav-border: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        .light-mode .mount-hero {
            background:
                radial-gradient(circle at 72% 32%, rgba(11, 116, 209, 0.16), transparent 34%),
                linear-gradient(135deg, #f7f9fc 0%, #edf6ff 52%, #f7f9fc 100%);
        }

        .light-mode .build-preview {
            background:
                linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.84)),
                url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591799264318-7e6ef8ddb7ea?auto=format&fit=crop&q=85&w=1000') center/cover;
        }

        .light-mode .preview-content {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.88);
        }

        .light-mode .lead-form {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.92);
            border-color: rgba(11, 116, 209, 0.22);
        }

        .light-mode .form-group label {
            color: #25415f;
        }

        .light-mode input,
        .light-mode select,
        .light-mode textarea {
            background: #ffffff;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            border-color: rgba(23, 32, 51, 0.14);
        }

        .light-mode .success-banner {
            background: rgba(21, 128, 61, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(21, 128, 61, 0.24);
            color: #166534;
        }

        .light-mode .build-card img {
            filter: saturate(1.06) contrast(1.02) brightness(1.03);
        }

        .light-mode .cta-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(160deg, rgba(11, 116, 209, 0.1), #ffffff);
        }

        .light-mode .nav-links a.active {
            color: #0b74d1;
            border-bottom-color: #0b74d1;
        }

        @media (max-width: 980px) {
            .mount-hero,
            .cta-panel {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .build-preview {
                min-height: 320px;
            }

            .lead-form {
                align-self: auto;
            }

            .build-grid,
            .workflow-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 720px) {
            .mount-hero {
                padding: 8rem 1.25rem 3rem;
                gap: 2rem;
            }

            .build-grid,
            .workflow-grid,
            .form-row {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }

            .section-heading {
                display: block;
            }

            .section-heading p {
                margin-top: 1rem;
            }

            .container {
                padding: 3rem 1.25rem;
            }

            footer {
                flex-direction: column;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('navbar') %>

    <header class="mount-hero">
        <div class="hero-copy">
            <div class="eyebrow">Montaje profesional</div>
            <h1>Tu equipo ideal, montado con <span>criterio técnico.</span></h1>
            <p>Diseñamos configuraciones equilibradas para gaming, edición, IA, oficina o estaciones profesionales. Sin piezas al azar: cada componente tiene una razón.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a class="btn-service btn-primary-service" href="#solicitud">Rellenar solicitud</a>
                <a class="btn-service" href="/hardware">Volver a hardware</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <form class="lead-form" id="solicitud" action="/solicitar-montaje" method="POST">
            <h2>Recibe una configuración inicial</h2>
            <p>Déjanos lo básico y te orientamos con una propuesta de montaje.</p>
            <% if (success) { %>
                <div class="success-banner">Solicitud enviada. Te responderemos lo antes posible.</div>
            <% } %>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="nombre">Nombre</label>
                    <input type="text" id="nombre" name="nombre" placeholder="Tu nombre" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="contacto">Contacto</label>
                    <input type="text" id="contacto" name="contacto" placeholder="Email o teléfono" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="presupuesto">Presupuesto</label>
                    <input type="text" id="presupuesto" name="presupuesto" placeholder="Ej: 1200€">
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="uso">Uso principal</label>
                    <select id="uso" name="uso">
                        <option value="">Selecciona una opción</option>
                        <option value="gaming">Gaming / Streaming</option>
                        <option value="edicion">Edición / 3D / IA</option>
                        <option value="oficina">Oficina / Empresa</option>
                        <option value="incerto">No estoy seguro</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="detalles">Qué necesitas</label>
                <textarea id="detalles" name="detalles" rows="3" placeholder="Piezas que tienes, uso, estética o dudas..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <button class="form-submit" type="submit">Solicitar montaje</button>
        </form>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
        <section id="tipos">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <h2>Configuraciones habituales</h2>
                <p>Estas son las bases más comunes. A partir de ahí ajustamos presupuesto, marcas, estética y necesidades reales.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="build-grid">
                <article class="build-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1591488320449-011701bb6704?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=900" alt="Componentes de PC gaming">
                    <div class="build-card-body">
                        <span class="build-tag">Gaming</span>
                        <h3>PC gaming y streaming</h3>
                        <p>FPS estables, buena refrigeración, GPU equilibrada y margen para futuras ampliaciones.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="build-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1518770660439-4636190af475?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=900" alt="Placa base y componentes electrónicos">
                    <div class="build-card-body">
                        <span class="build-tag green">Trabajo</span>
                        <h3>Edición, 3D e IA</h3>
                        <p>CPU, memoria, GPU y almacenamiento pensados para cargas pesadas y trabajo sostenido.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>

                <article class="build-card">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1516321318423-f06f85e504b3?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=900" alt="Portátil y espacio de trabajo profesional">
                    <div class="build-card-body">
                        <span class="build-tag amber">Empresa</span>
                        <h3>Equipos para oficina</h3>
                        <p>Silenciosos, rápidos y fiables para administración, ventas, atención al cliente y gestión diaria.</p>
                    </div>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="workflow">
            <div class="section-heading">
                <h2>Proceso de montaje</h2>
                <p>Un flujo claro para que sepas qué se decide, qué se compra y cómo se valida el equipo final.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="workflow-grid">
                <article class="workflow-step">
                    <strong>1</strong>
                    <h3>Uso y presupuesto</h3>
                    <p>Definimos para qué se usará el equipo y dónde conviene invertir.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="workflow-step">
                    <strong>2</strong>
                    <h3>Componentes</h3>
                    <p>Elegimos piezas compatibles y equilibradas, evitando cuellos de botella.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="workflow-step">
                    <strong>3</strong>
                    <h3>Montaje limpio</h3>
                    <p>Cableado ordenado, flujo de aire cuidado y BIOS configurada.</p>
                </article>
                <article class="workflow-step">
                    <strong>4</strong>
                    <h3>Pruebas</h3>
                    <p>Comprobamos temperaturas, estabilidad y rendimiento antes de entregar.</p>
                </article>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta-panel">
            <div>
                <h2>¿Tienes ya piezas o partes desde cero?</h2>
                <p>Podemos revisar una lista de componentes, proponer una configuración completa o montar un equipo con piezas que ya tengas.</p>
            </div>
            <a class="btn-service btn-primary-service" href="/hardware">Elegir servicio</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <div class="logo">TECHRM</div>
        <div>© 2026 TECHRM. Montaje claro, probado y preparado para crecer.</div>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
